  <brief_title>TaxXel: Taxotere and Xeloda in Esophageal Cancer</brief_title>
  <acronym>TaxXel</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase I/II Study on the Treatment With Taxotere in Combination With Xeloda in Patients With Metastatic Oesophageal Cancer or Cancer in the Cardia Region</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
